{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[{"categories":1,"event_categories":27},[2,9,15,21],{"id":3,"attributes":4},1,{"slug":5,"name":6,"description":7,"createdAt":8,"updatedAt":8},"nutrition","營養隨筆",null,"2023-02-07T08:03:25.893Z",{"id":10,"attributes":11},2,{"slug":12,"name":13,"description":7,"createdAt":14,"updatedAt":14},"spiritual","心靈勵志","2023-02-07T08:03:25.896Z",{"id":16,"attributes":17},3,{"slug":18,"name":19,"description":7,"createdAt":20,"updatedAt":20},"fitness","運動筆記","2023-02-07T08:03:25.905Z",{"id":22,"attributes":23},4,{"slug":24,"name":25,"description":7,"createdAt":26,"updatedAt":26},"reflection","感悟隨筆","2023-02-07T08:03:25.906Z",[28,33,38,43,47,52],{"id":3,"attributes":29},{"name":30,"slug":31,"description":7,"createdAt":32,"updatedAt":32},"名人面對面","be-our-guess","2023-02-07T08:03:24.223Z",{"id":10,"attributes":34},{"name":35,"slug":36,"description":7,"createdAt":37,"updatedAt":37},"文化導賞","cultural","2023-02-07T08:03:24.230Z",{"id":16,"attributes":39},{"name":40,"slug":41,"description":7,"createdAt":42,"updatedAt":42},"遊山玩水","hiking","2023-02-07T08:03:24.235Z",{"id":22,"attributes":44},{"name":45,"slug":5,"description":7,"createdAt":46,"updatedAt":46},"活學營養","2023-02-07T08:03:24.241Z",{"id":48,"attributes":49},5,{"name":50,"slug":18,"description":7,"createdAt":51,"updatedAt":51},"健體運動","2023-02-07T08:03:24.256Z",{"id":53,"attributes":54},6,{"name":55,"slug":56,"description":7,"createdAt":57,"updatedAt":57},"讀書會","book-sharing","2023-02-07T08:03:24.257Z"],"uses":{"dependencies":["http://localhost:1337/api/categories?","http://localhost:1337/api/event-categories?"]},"slash":"always"},{"type":"data","data":[{"id":1,"attributes":2},814,{"title":3,"excerpt":4,"content":5,"slug":6,"createdAt":7,"updatedAt":7,"author":8,"categories":15,"tags":23,"image":30,"related_posts":31},"運動前，有食的疑惑？",null,"\n\n運動與飲食的關係，迷思處處🧐。有人認為餓著做運動，會有更佳的消脂效果，真相是否如此🤔？\n\n餓著的，有早上一覺醒來，甚麼也不吃便出外做運動；睡了一夜，晚餐完全消化，身體處於肌餓狀態。也有下班後立即趕著做運動的，午餐後若沒再進食，加上工作消耗體能，身體能量就會大減😯。\n\n飢餓時，血糖濃度降低，未必有足夠能量供給身體應付運動需求，做運動時身體會較快感到疲倦，更有機會影響運動的專注力和表現，亦容易出現頭暈、無氣力等問題。\n\n最重要的是餓著做運動，更易造成肌肉流失😱。運動時，身體消耗大量能量，肌肉內的醣份會第一時間被使用，其次是以蛋白質作為能量來源。故此，若無適當補充，肌肉量會不增反降，造成基礎代謝率下降，養成易胖體質🥺，亦會影響運動表現。\u003Cbr\u003E\n因此，建議大家不要空肚做運動，而是運動前半小時至1小時，應該：\u003Cbr\u003E\n• 進食容易消化的低脂低纖食物，如蘋果、豆漿、天然果汁\u003Cbr\u003E\n• 避免攝取辛辣、刺激、纖維多的雜糧和易脹氣的豆類或牛奶，以免引起腸胃不適\u003Cbr\u003E\n• 吸收優質的蛋白質，研究證明能增加肌肉表現\n\n運動前切勿空肚，應適量進食，才能為身體提供充足能量及力氣，支撐整個運動過程，並提升運動質素。\n\nBy Ophelia Wong","food-before-exercise-220519","2022-05-19T00:00:00.000Z",{"data":9},{"id":10,"attributes":11},4,{"name":12,"slug":13,"profile":4,"createdAt":14,"updatedAt":14},"Melissa Wong","melissa","2023-02-07T08:03:28.224Z",{"data":16},[17],{"id":18,"attributes":19},3,{"slug":20,"name":21,"description":4,"createdAt":22,"updatedAt":22},"fitness","運動筆記","2023-02-07T08:03:25.905Z",{"data":24},[25],{"id":26,"attributes":27},157,{"name":28,"createdAt":29,"updatedAt":29},"運動飲食","2023-02-07T08:03:10.947Z",{"data":4},{"data":32},[]],"uses":{"dependencies":["http://localhost:1337/api/posts?populate[author]=true&populate[categories]=true&populate[tags]=true&populate[image]=true&populate[related_posts]=true&filters[slug][$eq]=food-before-exercise-220519"],"params":["slug"]}}]}